ERD
Customers (1) --- (M) Orders
Orders (1) --- (M) Order_Items
Order_Items (M) --- (1) Products
Products (M) --- (1) Categories
Orders (1) --- (1) Payments

Each order has one payment.
Visualizing the relationships:
Customers and Orders: One customer can place many orders.
Orders and Order_Items: An order can have many items.
Order_Items and Products: Many items can refer to one product.
Products and Categories: Products belong to a single category.
Orders and Payments: One order has one payment.


----------------data structure
bmshop/
│
├── config/
│   └── db.js       # Your database config (already provided)
│
├── models/
│   ├── Customer.js
│   ├── Product.js
│   ├── Category.js
│   ├── Order.js
│   ├── OrderItem.js
│   └── Payment.js
│
├── routes/
│   └── bmshopRoutes.js  # All CRUD routes
│
├── controllers/
│   └── bmshopController.js  # All CRUD logic
│
├── app.js  # Main app file
└── package.json
